  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pilot observational study to describe the relationship between the smoking status of a
      psoriatic individual and the success of etanercept therapy in psoriasis treatment
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      non-interventional study There is no sampling
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
